{"tid":258324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"法唔法國大陸賤婦成日係地鐵度阻撚住晒？","createTime":"2017-05-26T04:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T04:24:41.000Z","uid":32051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45731e8f8638aa2cf01bc5eb56c21a781b683089","tid":258324,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，見人用八達通do，你又學人do，出閘要插飛架，do你老母個閪咩。一係你就買張八達通用啦，買乜撚野飛。<br />\n柒撚懵懵咁，仲要幾隻臭雞嘈怨巴閉，塞撚住幾個閘口，研究你契家佬碌鳩啦，研究張單程飛點解do唔到出閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上落電梯又係柒撚懵懵，霸撚住晒唔撚識企埋一邊。落月台又扮撚晒爭分奪秒，企係度霸鳩住，兩邊望到底邊一邊方向上車。我屌你老母咩，你死落月台再睇清楚好過啦，塞撚住人。<br />\n<br />\n上到車，又塞撚住個車門，依樣唔係淨係你錯，香港都勁多仆街係咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸賤婦真係好撚阻礙社會運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9828a2c2f468e69c95552f7adb3eb6aa31fc18","tid":258324,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}